From: jxproxy <dev@jxproxy.dev>
Date: Thu, 02 Jul 2026 16:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Disable remote managed settings (phone-home)

Disables the remote managed settings system that polls
api.anthropic.com every hour for enterprise policy settings.
The eligibility check now always returns false, and all
entrypoint functions (load, refresh, polling) are no-ops.

This eliminates the phone-home mechanism and all associated
enterprise policy enforcement code paths from the binary.

